items.title: Awesome Blazor
items.content_text:
### ToDos

*   [TodoApi by David Fowler (⭐3k)](https://github.com/davidfowl/TodoApi) - ![stars](https://img.shields.io/github/stars/davidfowl/TodoApi?style=flat-square\&cacheSeconds=604800) ![last commit](https://img.shields.io/github/last-commit/davidfowl/TodoApi?style=flat-square\&cacheSeconds=86400) Todo application by David Fowler in .NET 7 that features an ASP.NET Core hosted Blazor WASM front end application and an ASP.NET Core REST API backend using minimal APIs.

### Tooling / Others

*   [LiveSharp (⭐77)](https://github.com/ionoy/LiveSharp) - ![stars](https://img.shields.io/github/stars/ionoy/LiveSharp?style=flat-square\&cacheSeconds=604800) ![last commit](https://img.shields.io/github/last-commit/ionoy/LiveSharp?style=flat-square\&cacheSeconds=86400) Update `.razor` files and see the updates instantly without reloading the page. Your application state is preserved because there is no need to reload anything. [livesharp.net](https://www.livesharp.net/).
items.content_html:
ToDos

  • TodoApi by David Fowler (⭐3k) - Todo application by David Fowler in .NET 7 that features an ASP.NET Core hosted Blazor WASM front end application and an ASP.NET Core REST API backend using minimal APIs.

Tooling / Others

  • LiveSharp (⭐77) - Update .razor files and see the updates instantly without reloading the page. Your application state is preserved because there is no need to reload anything. livesharp.net.

items.title: Awesome Yew
items.content_text:
### Projects

*   [theiskaa.com (⭐1)](https://github.com/theiskaa/theiskaa.com) - A real world implementation of Yew framework. [Live at theiskaa.com](https://theiskaa.com).
*   [live-ask.com (⭐103)](https://github.com/liveask/liveask) - Realtime Event/Meetup Q\&A Platform. [Live at live-ask.com](https://live-ask.com).

### Crates / Wasm

*   [tauri-sys (⭐108)](https://github.com/JonasKruckenberg/tauri-sys) - Raw bindings to the Tauri API for projects using wasm-bindgen.

### Tooling / Frameworks

*   [Tauri (⭐94k)](https://github.com/tauri-apps/tauri) - Tauri is a framework for building tiny, blazingly fast binaries for all major desktop platforms. Developers can integrate any front-end framework that compiles to HTML, JS and CSS for building their user interface. The backend of the application is a rust-sourced binary with an API that the front-end can interact with.
items.content_html:
Projects

  • theiskaa.com (⭐1) - A real world implementation of Yew framework. Live at theiskaa.com.
  • live-ask.com (⭐103) - Realtime Event/Meetup Q&A Platform. Live at live-ask.com.

Crates / Wasm

  • tauri-sys (⭐108) - Raw bindings to the Tauri API for projects using wasm-bindgen.

Tooling / Frameworks

  • Tauri (⭐94k) - Tauri is a framework for building tiny, blazingly fast binaries for all major desktop platforms. Developers can integrate any front-end framework that compiles to HTML, JS and CSS for building their user interface. The backend of the application is a rust-sourced binary with an API that the front-end can interact with.
